data.description: Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, you don't want to miss this 4 bedroom cape! Features include: an Incredible family room with vaulted ceilings that leads to the large back deck and yard perfect for entertaining; Newly Installed central AC; ALL new flooring with the 1st floor having hardwood with insulation beneath, and the 2nd floor having new carpeting; Remodeled full bath with marble floor; and whole house filtration system.  Newer roof, newer stainless steel appliances, and more.  Come call this house home!
